RecBoot for Mac:
-----------------
This Mac application was originally released almost a year ago. Today marks the day that Version 2 is available, completely open source.

However, there are a couple of issues with this at the moment.

When kicking the device into Recovery Mode and out of Recovery Mode in the same instance that the application is open, it will cause a crash.

Any help in resolving this crash would b e greatly appreciated.

FORK AWAY!

